{"tid":2155554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共軍宣布台海軍演   美軍機火速進駐沖繩　專家：美將更多動作","createTime":"2020-08-14T00:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T02:12:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa4474f6157d7b63b5d7f1a1c3c2283636a7100","tid":2155554,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T00:54:30.000Z","msg":"台灣與中國的關係向來緊張，中方也不時派軍機繞台，沒想到美國衛生部長艾薩（Alex Azar II）前腳才剛走，共軍東部戰區新聞發言人張春暉13日就表示，將出動多軍種在台海「實戰演練」，回擊一切製造台獨、分裂國家的挑釁行為，悍衛國家主權和領土完整。消息一出，引發各界討論，美軍也從美國派出軍機，飛往亞洲，進駐位於日本沖繩的嘉手納空軍基地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=796828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D796828&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=64dd2310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D796828&h=d0ec24a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=796828</a>"},{"pid":"ced83163a6217fc11d05158d6e31f4c0facc752d","tid":2155554,"uid":343361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T00:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b0583b9ddad7b9d09b8873cb0ffff5ae0a72593","tid":2155554,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d149